## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-160"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> それを実装するドキュメントの読み込みが完了する前にない呼び出さ 必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-160"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-161">ドキュメントが処理することによって読み込みを完了したときに検出することができます、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>イベント。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-161">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-162">次の例からドキュメントをスクリプト関数を呼び出す方法を示しています、[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]を使用してアプリケーション<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-162">The following example shows how to call a script function in a document from a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-163">この例では、スクリプト関数にはパラメーターがありません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-163">In this example, the script function has no parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-164">次に、[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)]から呼び出されるスクリプト関数を実装するドキュメント[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-164">The following is the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document that implements the script function that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function called!";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-165">次に示す、[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]実装で、スクリプト関数を呼び出す、[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)]ドキュメント。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-165">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script function in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters");  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-173"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> それを実装するドキュメントの読み込みが完了する前にない呼び出さ 必要があります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-173"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29> should not be called before the document that implements it has finished loading.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-174">ドキュメントが処理することによって読み込みを完了したときに検出することができます、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted>イベント。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-174">You can detect when a document has finished loading by handling the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.LoadCompleted> event.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-175">呼び出しているスクリプトに十分なパラメーター値を渡さない場合に値を渡すことのできないパラメーターが未定義の値になります。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-175">If you do not pass enough parameter values to the script that you are invoking, the parameters that you do not pass values to will have the undefined value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-176">渡すパラメーターの値が多すぎると、余分な値は無視されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-176">If you pass too many parameter values, the excess values are ignored.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-177">次の例を使用して、アプリケーションからドキュメントのスクリプトの関数を呼び出す方法を示しています。<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-177">The following example shows how to call script functions in a document from an application by using <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.InvokeScript%28System.String%2CSystem.Object%5B%5D%29>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-178">この例では、スクリプト機能には、パラメーターが必要です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-178">In this example, the script functions require parameters.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-179">次に、ドキュメントから呼び出されるスクリプトの関数を実装する[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-179">The following is the document that implements the script functions that will be called from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)].</span></span>  
  
```html  
<html>  
    <head>  
        <script type="text/javascript">  
            // Function Without Parameters  
            function JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters()    
            {  
              outputID.innerHTML = "JavaScript function 'called: " + message + ".";  
            }  
        </script>  
    </head>  
    <body>  
    <div id="outputID" style="color:Red; font-size:16">  
        Hello from HTML document with script!  
    </div>  
    </body>  
</html>  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-180">次に示す、[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)]関数を呼び出すスクリプトの実装、[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)]ドキュメント。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-180">The following shows the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_wpf](~/includes/tla2sharptla-wpf-md.md)] implementation to call the script functions in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_html](~/includes/tla2sharptla-html-md.md)] document.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
private void callScriptFunctionNoParamButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
  // Make sure the HTML document has loaded before attempting to  
  // invoke script of the document page. You could set loadCompleted  
  // to true when the LoadCompleted event on the WebBrowser fires.  
  if (this.loadCompleted)  
  {  
    try  
    {  
      this.webBrowser.InvokeScript("JavaScriptFunctionWithoutParameters", this.messageTextBox.Text);  
    }  
    catch (Exception ex)  
    {  
      string msg = "Could not call script: " +  
                   ex.Message +  
                  "\n\nPlease click the 'Load HTML Document with Script' button to load.";  
      MessageBox.Show(msg);  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-194">呼び出す<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29>設定と同じ効果があります、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A>プロパティ。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-194">Calling <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> has the same effect as setting the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-195"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> ドキュメントの最初の宣言で指定する開発者向けのマークアップから設定される<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>が移動するときに<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>が初期化されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-195"><xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Source%2A> is used from markup by developers who want to declaratively specify the initial document that <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> navigates to when <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> is initialized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-196">使用して、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29>メソッドをエスケープ文字を含めることができますを URL に移動します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-196">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-197">使用して、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29>に移動する方法、<xref:System.Uri>エスケープ文字は含まれていません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-197">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-198">次の例は、使用する方法を示します<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser>を使用して、ドキュメントに移動する、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29>メソッド。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-198">The following example shows how to use <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser> to navigate to a document by using the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%29> method.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute eg 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri);  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-216">使用して、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29>メソッドをエスケープ文字を含めることができますを URL に移動します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-216">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.String%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a URL that may include escape characters.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-217">使用して、<xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29>に移動する方法、<xref:System.Uri>エスケープ文字は含まれていません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-217">Use the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.WebBrowser.Navigate%28System.Uri%2CSystem.String%2CSystem.Byte%5B%5D%2CSystem.String%29> method to navigate to a <xref:System.Uri> that does not include escape characters.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="e9ead-218">次の例では、ドキュメントに移動し、指定することで、新しいブラウザー ウィンドウで開く方法、"について: 空白"ターゲット。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e9ead-218">The following example shows how to navigate to a document and open it in a new browser window by specifying the "about:blank" target.</span></span>  
  
```xaml  
<StackPanel>  
    <StackPanel Orientation="Horizontal">  
        <TextBox x:Name="addressTextBox" Width="200" />  
        <Button Click="goNavigateButton_Click">Go</Button>  
    </StackPanel>  
    <WebBrowser x:Name="myWebBrowser" />  
</StackPanel>  
```  
  
```csharp  
private void goNavigateButton_Click(object sender, RoutedEventArgs e)  
{  
    // Get URI to navigate to  
    Uri uri = new Uri(this.addressTextBox.Text, UriKind.RelativeOrAbsolute);  
  
    // Only absolute URIs can be navigated to  
    if (!uri.IsAbsoluteUri)  
    {  
        MessageBox.Show("The Address URI must be absolute eg 'http://www.microsoft.com'");  
        return;  
    }  
  
    // Navigate to the desired URL by calling the .Navigate method  
    this.myWebBrowser.Navigate(uri, "_blank", null, null);  
}  
```

  
  
